  "title": "Practice Tips for Playing Songs",
  "lessonText": "Here are some essential tips to enhance your song-playing practice.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Start slow: Focus on accuracy before speed.\n- Use a metronome: Keep your timing consistent.\n- Break it down: Practice difficult sections separately.\n- Repeat regularly: Consistency is key for improvement.\n- Record yourself: Listen for areas to improve.\n- Stay relaxed: Tension can hinder your playing.\n- Enjoy the process: Play songs you love to stay motivated."
  }
}
